item.title: CVE-2021-24142|2024-08-03T19:21:18.295Z -- unknown -- 301%20redirects%20-%20easy%20redirect%20manager
item.description: Unvaludated input in the 301 Redirects - Easy Redirect Manager WordPress plugin, versions before 2.51, did not sanitise its "Redirect From" column when importing a CSV file, allowing high privilege users to perform SQL injections.
